  - US3 (View Tasks) ‚Üí Can start after Phase 2, requires auth from US2
  - US4 (Add Task) ‚Üí Can start after Phase 2, requires US3 for display
  - US5 (Toggle Complete) ‚Üí Can start after Phase 2, requires US3 for display
  - US6 (Update Task) ‚Üí Can start after Phase 2, requires US3 for display
  - US7 (Delete Task) ‚Üí Can start after Phase 2, requires US3 for display
